::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610907-->
::::'''Montana:''' Oh right! When I was checking on the stage equipment, I noticed there was an unfinished track inside.
::::'''Montana:''' Maybe Lady Rappa left it behind? I'm not too sure either... but if you can collect enough composition inspiration, the remaining band members might be able to finish the track.
::::'''Montana:''' Give it a try! The stage show is going to continue, so it'd be a bigger blast with new music!
