:::{{DIcon|Talk}} The band's reviews...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610911-->
::::'''Montana:''' That closing show at the end was deffo the most exciting performance I've ever witnessed, bar none!
::::'''Montana:''' Lady Rappa's surprise reveal, everyone else's freestyling, and the showdown between the Festive Superstar and the academy's representative... It's spread across the school like wildfire, and everyone on campus can't stop talking about it!
::::'''Montana:''' *sigh* After witnessing such a powerful performance, the other celebration activities appear bland in comparison.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the music party...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610915-->
::::'''Montana:''' The music party is the grandest event of the Dreamlight Anniversary celebration. It's also a time that all students look forward to!
::::'''Montana:''' Everyone is busy preparing for the celebration, and the campus is filled with fun booths and activities. Just wandering around is enough to make you feel overwhelmed. Freedom and joy &mdash; this is what the atmosphere of a college should feel like.
::::'''Montana:''' Needless to say... there's also such an exciting performance!
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_802610239_106-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_802610239_106-->
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} How long will the music party last?
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610919-->
:::::'''Montana:''' According to past experience, the music party and the Dreamlight Anniversary celebration will end at the same time. But there are people who are constantly asking for the event time to be extended. No one really knows for sure how long this will last.
:::::'''Montana:''' As for us, of course, we'd like it to last as long as possible.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} The music party is related to the three academies?
